# ============================================================
# .gitignore RACINE — C'EMPIRE PROJECT
# Protège l'ensemble du repo contre les fuites de secrets
# ============================================================

# --- Fichiers d'environnement (NE JAMAIS COMMITER) ---
.env
.env.*
!.env.*.example
!.env.example

# --- Secrets et clés privées ---
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
*.cert
*.crt
secrets/
credentials/

# --- Config runtime frontend (généré au déploiement) ---
frontend/public/config.js

# --- Dépendances ---
**/node_modules/

# --- Build outputs ---
**/dist/
**/build/

# --- Logs ---
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*

# --- Caches ---
**/.angular/cache
**/.cache/

# --- Uploads utilisateurs ---
**/uploads/

# --- Outils IDE ---
.vscode/
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea/
*.suo
*.user

# --- OS ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# --- Coverage / tests ---
**/coverage/
**/playwright-report/
**/test-results/

# --- Docker ---
.vercel/
